title: Rolling Stones  - Live 1965 Charlie Is My Darling (2014)
description:
"Charlie Is My Darling - Ireland 1965" was the first documentary film about the Rolling Stones. The film was shot during the band's second tour of Ireland on September 3 & 4, 1965.
The restored version premiered at the 2012 New York Film Festival, and was released on DVD and Blu-ray in November 2012.
